@1574 = ~Quayle talks for a good hour about how he apprenticed in the arts of magic and the worship of Baravar Cloakshadow under a gnome named Gifos and how he was apparently encouraged to strike out on his own and create the Circus of Chaos because, as he claims, he was simply too gifted to remain in the stifling environment of adventuring. He then talks for another hour about the problems of running a circus in a city like Athkatla and decides that he is simply too intelligent and useful to be left behind and is doing you a favor by helping you.~
