@1576 = ~Tiax~
@1577 = ~When asked about his past, Tiax ignores you entirely, preferring instead to loudly proclaim what is in store for his future. He obviously still worships Cyric, his madness has grown exponentially. Tiax unquestioningly believes that he is destined to rule the world, and his fervor makes him blind to the ridiculous nature of the goal. He seems harmless enough for now, but has been increasingly talking about bringing down the Spellweave with the avatar of Shar.~

